  "title": "Public Schools \u2013 Content Standards, Curriculum, and Bullying Policies \u2013 Culture and History of Palestine",
  "summary": "Requiring the State Board of Education to develop certain content standards regarding the culture and history of Palestine to be included in certain State standards for social studies; requiring the Department to develop certain curriculum guides and instructional resources regarding the culture and history of Palestine in alignment with certain content standards; requiring each public school to include Palestinian culture and history in the social studies curriculum beginning in the 2027-2028 school year; etc.",
